title: 1935 Noir | Danger Ahead — Crime never rests, and neither will you - A Sam Katzman film

sources.title: 1935 Noir | Danger Ahead — Crime never rests, and neither will you - A Sam Katzman film
sources.description:
A sea captain receives $40,000 from a crook, and the crooks try to steal it from him.

Director: Albert Herman
Producer: Sam Katzman

Main actors:
Lawrence Gray - Jerry Mason, reporter
Sheila Bromley - Lorraine Matthews, Captain's daughter
J. Farrell MacDonald - Harry Cromwell, the city editor
Fuzzy Knight - Fred Klein the butcher
Bryant Washburn - Nick Conrad the gangster
Fred Kelsey - Detective O'Brien
John Elliott - Captain Matthews
Eddie Phillips - Eddie, henchman
Arthur Loft - Pete, balding henchman
Herschel Mayall - Steve, henchman
Gordon Griffith - Chuck, henchman
Earl Dwire - Detective Sergeant
Richard Cramer - Detective Hogan
George Chesebro - First Mate Taylor

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/c2HDPvQo_6k

Release date: July 19, 1935
Filming location: Los Angeles, California, USA
